T02D2123:170a-1: shr'i ae ka rdza t'i bha ga w'a na s'a dha nam /
T02D2123:170a-3: dpal bcom ldan 'das ral ba gcig pa'i sgrub thabs /
T02D2123:170a-4: rje btsun ral pa pa gcig pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2123:170a-5: dang por re zhig sngags pas tshogs bsags pa sngon du 'gro bas padma dang /
T02D2123:170a-7: ro'i gdan bltas la de'i steng du h'um dang bam
T02D2123:170b-0: las yab dang yum ral pa @170b gcig 'phyang pa'i
T02D2123:170b-4: byang gi padma'i 'dab ma dag la ni rdo rje 'khor lo dang /
T02D2123:170b-7: rdo rje sna tshogs rnams bsam mo //
T02D2123:170b-8: byang shar la sogs pa'i mtshams bzhir ni bdud rtsi ka p'a la dag go //
T02D2123:170b-9: de'i phyi rol du khyams kyi phyogs bzhir gti mug
T02D2123:170b-10: rdo rje ma dkar mo sgron ma thogs pa dang
T02D2123:170b-11: / bag chags rdo rje ma ser mo rdo rje thogs pa dang /
T02D2123:170b-12: 'dod chags rdo rje ma dmar mo zhags pa thogs pa dang /
T02D2123:170b-13: zhe sdang rdo rje ma ljang gu ral gri thogs pa rnams bsgom mo //
T02D2123:170b-14: khyams gyi grva bzhir ni byang shar nas brtsams te
T02D2123:170b-15: brtan pa'i rdo rje ma ser mo ri rab thogs
T02D2123:170b-16: pa dang / sbyor ba'i rdo rje ma dkar mo zla ba thogs pa dang /
T02D2123:170b-17: 'bar ba'i rdo rje ma dmar mo nyi ma thogs pa dang /
T02D2123:170b-18: stobs kyi rdo rje ma ljang gu ba dang thogs pa rnams dgod do //
T02D2123:170b-19: brgyad po 'di dag ni padma dang ro'i gdan la rnam par dgod pa yin no //
T02D2123:170b-22: byang gi sgo bzhir yang go rims ltar rdo rje lcags kyu dang /
T02D2123:170b-25: dril bu 'dzin pa rnams dkar ba dang /
T02D2123:170b-28: ljang gu'i mdog can rnams bsgom par bya'o //
T02D2123:170b-29: ji ltar dam tshig bskyed pa dang /
T02D2123:170b-30: ye shes sems dpa' gzhug pa nyid /
T02D2123:170b-31: gsang sngags bzlas shing bsgom pa dang //
T02D2123:170b-32: rdzogs pa'i rim sogs cho ga bzhin //
T02D2123:170b-33: dpal bcom ldan 'das ral pa gcig pa'i man ngag khungs phyung ba /
T02D2123:170b-34: slob dpon chen po mi pham sbas pas bsdus pa rdzogs so /
T02D2123:170b-36: // / rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug shr'i mi tra dang /
